gogetfunding.com%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%259C%25BE%25E5%25BF%2597%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%25E7%259C%25BE%25E7%25B1%258C%25E8%25A8%2588%25E5%258A%2583-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project%2F%3Fshow_desktop%3D1&d=kAMrkm0lh8tAzahNx%2FKaSJKhd8YmQljH21R%2F5cbT5WU%3D&h=0fa036e5\" target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E7%9C%BE%E7%B1%8C%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project/?show_desktop=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">什麼是遊說集團？</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">遊說集團的工作，<strong><ins>是嘗試影響立法者</ins></strong>或其他持份者決定或行為，在政治角力中為服務對象<strong><ins>爭取利益</ins></strong>。遊說集團的服務對象，可以是國家、企業、社會團體、個人。在美國，政治遊說是極為普遍及重要的一環；幾乎所有政治操作都有遊說集團的參與。</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">為什麼香港需要遊說隊伍？</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">任何國家的政治，背後都擁有複雜的政治脈絡；包括國家政策、政治形勢、民意、錯綜複雜的利益網絡、乃至個別官員或議員的性情喜好。要在國際社會維護和爭取香港的利益，<strong><ins>香港需要一支能具經驗和技巧，能夠有效收風、熟識政治形勢</ins></strong>、具備遊說策略的隊伍。</span>"},{"pid":"9f58950da0651eab05941f16f277819b95377f73","tid":1668853,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T09:45:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"12667e42574dbd9b849fd853da2a057015ff268a","tid":1668853,"uid":254594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T10:07:13.000Z","msg":"聽講二戰德軍坦克雖然好厚甲，但因為行汽油所以好怕汽油彈<br />\n唔知今日狗隊裝甲車又怕唔怕汽油彈呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8b66c657731b47a8be64c9cb263866d3eccb011","tid":1668853,"uid":131157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T10:18:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 